caption:
Have you been to @eastrockcoffeeshop yet? Garden City finally has a spot that does it all — coffee, cocktails, and full entrées. 

From steak & eggs and chicken & waffles to mimosa flights and espresso martini flights (Classic, Toasted Marshmallow, Baileys, Mocha)… this is the place to brunch, sip, and celebrate this fall🍁

And don’t forget the seasonal drinks — Fall in a Cup, Cinnamon Blast, and Almond Joy with coconut. Perfect for cozy days here at @eastrockcoffeeshop 

📍 East Rock Coffee Shop – Garden City, NY
✨ More than a café. It’s brunch, it’s cocktails, it’s your next go-to spot.
